    <p>This is the <em>technical documentation</em> for the Sámi
    pedagogical system <em>Oahpa!</em>.</p>

    <p>Our documentation for end users, i.e. for teachers, pupils and students
      is found at <a
    href="http://giellatekno.uit.no/oahpa">giellatekno.uit.no/oahpa/</a>. That documentation
     is in Sámi, Norwegian and English. User 
    documentation in Finnish is forthcoming, but later.</p>

